	$$\frac{\delta }{\delta x}e^y=1$$
	$$\frac{\delta y}{\delta x}e^y=1$$
	$$\frac{\delta y}{\delta x}x=1$$
	$$\frac{\delta y}{\delta x}=\frac{1}{x}$$

